data.description: Beautifully updated, freshly painted 3 bdrm, 2 bath home w/ car port! Great open kitchen w/ quartz countertops, Stainless Steel appliances, & exquisite waterproof vinyl flooring throughout. The primary bedroom is complete w/ its own separate entrance, ensuite bathroom, & walk in closet. The dining room has a custom chandelier & lovely French door leading you to a spacious backyard with a pergola, solid storage unit & plenty of room for a pool. Property is walking distance to pickle ball courts, multiple parks & the downtown; the city hosts multiple events all year. Oakland Park is building a state-of-the-art city hall, fire station, community center and so much more. Oversized driveway w plenty of parking for guests & space to park all your toys. Call today!
